1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:30,040
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:32,589
=Episode 2=
(Deep love brings deep sorrow.)

3
00:00:32,590 --> 00:00:35,420
(Even in clear skies, hatred runs deep.)

4
00:00:37,540 --> 00:00:39,220
For a hundred years,

5
00:00:41,020 --> 00:00:42,779
day and night...

6
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:43,940
No!

7
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:45,380
No!

8
00:00:45,580 --> 00:00:48,220
I've waited for this moment.

9
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:49,740
No!

10
00:01:05,780 --> 00:01:07,340
The Universe is heartless,

11
00:01:07,420 --> 00:01:09,459
viewing all life
as mere sacrificial dust.

12
00:01:09,460 --> 00:01:11,819
Gods are void of emotion.

13
00:01:11,820 --> 00:01:14,219
and they certainly hold no love
or hate for a demon.

14
00:01:14,220 --> 00:01:16,340
You, however, are quite different.

15
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:19,580
(Heavenly Dao)
You're one of my few failed creations.

16
00:01:19,780 --> 00:01:21,420
Old man of the Heavenly Dao,

17
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:24,460
I've killed that demon.

18
00:01:24,900 --> 00:01:27,339
From now on, I answer to no one.

19
00:01:27,340 --> 00:01:29,340
Who are you talking to?

20
00:01:32,460 --> 00:01:34,140
That demon isn't dead.

21
00:01:34,660 --> 00:01:35,779
What?

22
00:01:35,780 --> 00:01:38,460
I just destroyed her demon heart.

23
00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:40,900
She should be dead.

24
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:43,419
If the demon root remains,

25
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:45,100
the demon heart can't truly die.

26
00:01:45,220 --> 00:01:46,259
Demon root?

27
00:01:46,260 --> 00:01:49,020
Demon root will grow another heart.

28
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:57,040
(Ning Palace)

29
00:01:57,280 --> 00:02:00,200
(Emperor of Ning, Chu Shan)

30
00:02:02,220 --> 00:02:04,580
Your Majesty.

31
00:02:06,820 --> 00:02:07,899
Rise.

32
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:09,060
Yes, Your Majesty.

33
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:11,579
Your Majesty. Recently,
a group of strange figures

34
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:13,040
has been abducting civilians
in Ning Capital.

35
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,980
I'm already aware.

36
00:02:15,020 --> 00:02:17,220
You will handle this matter in full.

37
00:02:17,260 --> 00:02:18,139
Yes, Your Majesty.

38
00:02:18,140 --> 00:02:19,579
The Golden-Masked Guard reports

39
00:02:19,580 --> 00:02:21,780
that Chu Xihe is missing.

40
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:24,019
Find her.

41
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:25,580
Yes, Your Majesty.

42
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:55,100
Why have you abducted me

43
00:02:55,460 --> 00:02:57,060
and brought me here?

44
00:02:58,660 --> 00:03:00,780
You failed to tempt me,

45
00:03:02,420 --> 00:03:04,940
and now you pretend nothing happened?

46
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:06,780
My dear wife.

47
00:03:07,900 --> 00:03:10,180
Impressive tactics.

48
00:03:12,100 --> 00:03:14,940
I am the princess of Ning.

49
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:16,660
Why would I seduce you?

50
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:24,860
How could a mortal blade

51
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:29,940
harm a god?

52
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:38,420
I don't care whether
you're human or god.

53
00:03:39,300 --> 00:03:40,860
You're nothing

54
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:43,060
but a madman to me.

55
00:03:47,740 --> 00:03:49,860
I am a madman indeed.

56
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:56,060
A madman who's driven to death

57
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:01,780
by the one I loved most.

58
00:04:04,380 --> 00:04:06,220
Where is

59
00:04:07,660 --> 00:04:09,740
your demon root?

60
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:19,740
I've never heard of such a thing.

61
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:22,220
You've got the wrong person.

62
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:25,420
Are you saying

63
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:28,500
I'm accusing you wrongly?

64
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,820
Even if you kill me,

65
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:35,260
I still don't know what you mean.

66
00:04:49,660 --> 00:04:51,060
Bound by hair,

67
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:55,500
you take your vows.

68
00:04:56,340 --> 00:04:58,220
I now pronounce you husband and wife,

69
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:00,180
bound in love for all eternity.

70
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:17,740
It doesn't matter.

71
00:05:18,540 --> 00:05:19,860
I'm not in a hurry.

72
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:22,260
I have my ways.

73
00:05:23,300 --> 00:05:25,300
Stay here in this hall.

74
00:05:25,860 --> 00:05:27,500
I'll search you,

75
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:30,740
inch by inch,

76
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:35,300
through your flesh and bones,

77
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:40,420
until I find your demon root.

78
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:51,419
If you dare take one step
outside Baihua Hall,

79
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:53,660
I'll cut off your limbs

80
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:58,140
and turn you into a crippled shell.

81
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:20,300
You've gone soft again.

82
00:06:25,590 --> 00:06:29,130
♪I too once lost myself for ages♪

83
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:31,739
Since you know everything,

84
00:06:31,740 --> 00:06:34,060
why won't you tell me
where the demon root is?

85
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:36,660
(Within the Three Realms,)

86
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:40,860
(only you and her can find it.)

87
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,219
♪You fall into my gaze♪

88
00:06:43,220 --> 00:06:45,669
♪Yet mistaken for the moon♪

89
00:06:45,670 --> 00:06:48,289
♪I break through fate's cocoon♪

90
00:06:48,290 --> 00:06:52,289
♪Travel a thousand miles to you♪

91
00:06:52,290 --> 00:06:54,979
♪You are a night of falling petals♪

92
00:06:54,980 --> 00:06:59,129
♪Gone in a blink,
you fade to the horizon♪

93
00:06:59,130 --> 00:07:05,790
♪Telling me not to long for you♪

94
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:10,660
(She's feigning pity.)

95
00:07:51,660 --> 00:07:52,820
Mother,

96
00:07:53,580 --> 00:07:55,460
please don't abandon me.

97
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:06,019
Xihe,

98
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:07,779
he's a monster who rips out hearts.

99
00:08:07,780 --> 00:08:08,940
Leave at once.

100
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:10,300
Mother!

101
00:08:21,440 --> 00:08:26,099
(Qingxin Pavilion)

102
00:08:26,100 --> 00:08:27,980
Your fever hasn't subsided,

103
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:30,100
and you're leaving already?

104
00:08:40,290 --> 00:08:42,660
I warned you before.

105
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:44,720
If you dare run,

106
00:08:45,540 --> 00:08:48,380
I'll turn you into a crippled shell.

107
00:08:50,060 --> 00:08:51,220
(This is bad.)

108
00:09:11,310 --> 00:09:13,019
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

109
00:09:13,020 --> 00:09:15,869
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

110
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:18,609
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

111
00:09:18,610 --> 00:09:20,239
♪Let the long shadows♪

112
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:25,840
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

113
00:09:25,890 --> 00:09:27,489
♪If in a dream♪

114
00:09:27,490 --> 00:09:30,249
♪I can hear your voice♪

115
00:09:30,250 --> 00:09:33,099
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

116
00:09:33,100 --> 00:09:35,699
♪Let it be us♪

117
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:40,489
♪drawing endlessly close♪

118
00:09:40,490 --> 00:09:42,249
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

119
00:09:42,250 --> 00:09:44,900
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

120
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:47,839
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

121
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,489
♪Not even in time♪

122
00:09:49,490 --> 00:09:55,149
♪to tell you how I feel♪

123
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:56,689
♪If the rain won't stop♪

124
00:09:56,690 --> 00:09:59,439
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

125
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:02,409
♪Let love go on♪

126
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:04,959
♪Until forever♪

127
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:09,599
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

128
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:12,209
♪Until forever♪

129
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:19,320
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
